<h3>
<a name="computer-science-academy" class="anchor" href="#computer-science-academy"><span class="octicon octicon-link"></span></a>Computer Science Academy (CSA)</h3>

<ul>
<li>Courses focus on learning computer science concepts through inquiry and projects.</li>
<li>Themes and practices include the creative nature of computing, problem-solving using technology as a tool, and seeing the relevance and impact of computer science.</li>
<li>Students in CSA take their Computer Science class and their English class together with the same students. The teachers work to build projects and skills across the curriculum â€“ together we form a small learning community.</li>
<li>College and career skills are built into the courses to prepare students for higher education and future work as computing professionals.</li>
</ul>

